<SYNC Start=572051><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=572052><P Class=ENCC>
저, 나쁜 짓은 하지 않았어요
<SYNC Start=575904><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577532><P Class=ENCC>
